{"tid":452941,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"8號波一定飛唔到？超強颱風有幾強？想知颱風多d就入黎啦","createTime":"2017-10-30T16:42:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T02:52:13.000Z","uid":38255,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"14964550c79e30cbc5a2d9d1d20907ca3c696f03","tid":452941,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T16:42:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/31/003546_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F31%2F003546_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b342c67a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港又打風？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/31/003444_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F31%2F003444_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ff0f1782&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咪玩啦去越南架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解個風超強但香港得1號波？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解明明個風行得離香港咁遠又會8號波而且真係幾大風？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日聽到東登西登又係咩黎？東登定西登對香港有幾重要？影響差幾遠又點解會咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n星期六日或者夜晚掛8仔/紅黑雨係咪真係會鬆手d？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上面果兩幅圖又應該點正確解讀呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有咁多疑問又想知道答案既巴絲有福啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連登氣象台三位巴打將會係黎緊星期六為大家一一解答，其中一位巴打仲曾經為香港天文台工作，到時會分享工作點滴同天文台既有趣小秘密<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當中包括香港天文台內部點睇澳門果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n很想要吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家就快d去報名啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 名額有限，full左就唔知幾時再有機會架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n～～～～～～～～～～～～～～～～～～<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">日期：11月4日(星期六)<br />\n時間：15：00 - 17：00</span><br />\n講者：3位<br />\n名額：12人<br />\n主題：連登氣象台 - 颱風速成班<br />\n～～～～～～～～～～～～～～～～～～<br />\n<br />\n報名請係telegram聯絡以下巴打　<a href=\"http://telegram.me/DuskoZutic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.me%2FDuskoZutic&d=UL5cvNv%2F1Ejd2ki1%2FK2IKf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=761c5cdc\" target=\"_blank\">telegram.me/DuskoZutic</a><br />\n然後留低以下資訊：<br />\n<br />\n稱呼：<br />\n人數：<br />\n聯絡電話：<br />\n分享會主題： <br />\n<br />\n名額先到先得，如報名後無法出席請盡早通知，可以騰個位比其他人<br />\n活動本身無收費，希望每位參與者都可以帶少少飲品同食物上黎同其他人分享。<br />\n地址會係活動日期前一日通知大家，地區係葵興。謝謝大家。"},{"pid":"d63fb9cba4dc8841b84f25532dd204268a2fe0bd","tid":452941,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T17:35:03.000Z","msg":"最衰嗰日唔得閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw，樓主係咪講者之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d768f6b7ceb48320e9a9401ea456f97727ba137","tid":452941,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T17:39:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最衰嗰日唔得閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw，樓主係咪講者之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 另外兩位巴打係<br />\n道地檸檬綠茶，一個地球人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf28ef5728a5dcc311a619baac6750a33b4dc60","tid":452941,"uid":63303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T19:17:42.000Z","msg":"星期六要返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f224cc65a91380eb6b9c70d6b5592838e1efa17","tid":452941,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T22:01:37.000Z","msg":"留個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c66b4808720161ecacaac74b719064bf2740ae5a","tid":452941,"uid":43178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T23:25:02.000Z","msg":"我有冇得參加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c68e34e91fed3fc1a0a7fffc68b7c67ccebf5397","tid":452941,"uid":44630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T00:06:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我有冇得參加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n快d報名啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70d3742cf54a4da83dd4bff49448128c0d469f9b","tid":452941,"uid":38255,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T05:41:48.000Z","msg":"11月都打風？　菲以東現低壓區稍後進入南海<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171031/bkn-20171031115249272-1031_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171031%2Fbkn-20171031115249272-1031_00822_001.html&d=UL5cvNv%2F1Ejd2ki1%2FK2IKf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=1b578004\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171031/bkn-20171031115249272-1031_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>秋意漸深，但天文台九天天氣預報指出，菲律賓以東海域出現低壓區，並會在本周後期進入南海中至南部。台灣中央氣象局亦指，位於南海及菲律賓以東海面的熱帶擾動，未來不排除有進一步發展的可能。莫非11月還會打風？ <br />\n<br />\n另外，香港天文台資料顯示，對上一次11月份有颱風吹襲香港，已是2013年11月1日，當時強颱風「羅莎」吹襲，天文台發出1號戒備信號。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n竟然真係有報紙吹奏呢個武雷宮咁遠既會打風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n報紙佬係咪認為入南海就一定關香港事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n天文台會講離香港1000公里外既南海南部多多少少係因為畀行船既睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想以後自己唔再畀報紙佬呃識得自己睇會唔會打風，各位就要黎學野捧場啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f8ad68137346ba72a0b7d37dc499f9cb04cebb0","tid":452941,"uid":44630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T15:52:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d66b63c48a4c4312d2bcec616f0349dfee3174e7","tid":452941,"uid":37210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T16:34:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13cd08b9a70b6acdc818a5b6e37a40e91f3ef100","tid":452941,"uid":69679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T18:25:23.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一對四小班教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n做到眾人皆智者，就可以百分之一百謠言止於智者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去秦國灣個TC真係關香港叉事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#世上太多假嘢流料 #拒絕報道失實不可靠消息來源 #你真係肯定11月都打風？"},{"pid":"5f1c5609f69961138cbba42c727534cdeb45663c","tid":452941,"uid":8089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T23:45:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid